i have a question, though, when you say</p>
<p>4. Continue to check the mixture every 30 minutes, stirring vigorously as it&#8217;s freezing. If you have one, you can use a hand-held mixer for best results, or use a stick-blender or hand-held mixer.</p>
<p>won&#8217;t it turn to mush if i use a stick-blender?</p>
