	<div class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-62253">
		<div class="comauth"><span class="byline">By <span class="comauthor">jay</span> on <a href="http://www.davidlebovitz.com/2007/07/making-ice-crea-1/comment-page-1/#comment-62253">October 1, 2010 10:18 PM</a></span></div>
